{"tid":1954852,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［JJ插熔岩］電腦問題 求救","createTime":"2020-04-02T06:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T06:45:34.000Z","uid":136699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"66fc44e843b466bcb4c978894ba0c1bd11e6c117","tid":1954852,"uid":136699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHtHrXL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHtHrXL.png&h=52e0f022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身一開機出現呢個畫面都成個月 我見撳咗F1之後入下邊幅圖度就啟動到 所以我冇理佢繼續用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UjGJVRF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUjGJVRF.png&h=c867eecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係今日我下載野嘅時候 部電腦就自動重新開機 跟住重新開機完之後我再下載多次又自動重新開機<br />\n但係呢次重新開機就開唔番部電腦 <br />\n上網查過好似係硬碟問題 咁我係唔係淨係換左個硬碟就得？"},{"pid":"e89064782255dd37b90b89a061dd6b8a73cb5f76","tid":1954852,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"4c1218d597c3aefa2546945a806aeaf4456405ce","tid":1954852,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"當然啦 又有可能係SATA線或者SATA頭有問題"},{"pid":"bc6d03047456d7eaa92a4027e10d37ea320e8139","tid":1954852,"uid":136699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c1218d597c3aefa2546945a806aeaf4456405ce","tid":1954852,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"當然啦 又有可能係SATA線或者SATA頭有問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"有冇辦法可以自己檢查到係咪條線有問題"},{"pid":"284c2ddb48bd46eb4a7ba441f204c296975f3414","tid":1954852,"uid":284932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"以前就有張 PCI / ISA Debug 咭"},{"pid":"c3706ffb2ce6388945acc51cba4cf5b6cdffa92c","tid":1954852,"uid":284932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"或者淨係買張 PCI 既 SATA  controller card  囉<br /